&lt;h3 id="clear-output"&gt;Clear Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;clear_output&lt;/code&gt; when set to true will remove all files in the destination folder prior to importing the data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ie. if fetching all dashboards for the default org, then all files in the folder: &lt;code&gt;{output_path}/org_main-org/dashboards&lt;/code&gt; will be removed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout-caution d-flex flex-row mt-4 mb-4 pt-4 pe-4 pb-2 ps-3"&gt;
 &lt;svg
 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
